language Essence 1.3
given n : int
letting vertices be domain int(1..n)
given G : set of set (size 2) of vertices

letting colours be new type of size n
find f : function vertices --> colours
such that forAll e in G . f(min(e)) != f(max(e))

find c : int(1..n) such that c = |toSet([ f(u) | u : vertices ])|
minimising c
